    <description>GT-19 / US-022: Fires when pro_Yes_No__c or pro_Provided_By__c changes on a checklist item. Collects changed item IDs and calls pro_ConditionalChecklistGenerator to create or deactivate dependent items based on CMDT-configured dependencies.</description>
